</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Cheese with bread in a dream is a journey to the sea, far from home, and great difficulties and little profit</p>
<p>Cheese with honey in a dream means <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money </a> and excess profit and little effort</p>
<p>Cheese with milk or yogurt succeeds in many things, and it is said about him that he is famous and has money, and it is said that it is a marriage of convenience or a debt spent</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
