</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Cheese with dates is an increase in knowledge with an increase in livelihood</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Cheese with apples in a dream is a benefit that will be spent or a crisis that will pass peacefully</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
