</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In case the girl feels confused and hesitant at that time to accept or reject a proposal of marriage, she can agree to this engagement after seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-سورة-النصر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=862" > Surah An-Nasr </a>, because it calls her to it and she hopes that he will be a righteous and devout young man who will work by God's command to provide her with comfort and safety. </p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-سورة-النصر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=862" > Surah An-Nasr </a> in a dream for a married woman</strong></h2>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-سورة-النصر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=862" > Surah An-Nasr </a> indicates many verses for a married woman, and it may bring her good or warn her of evil, and some interpreters have mentioned that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-سورة-النصر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين-والنابلسي?page=862" > Surah An-Nasr </a> is evidence of the removal of worries and rulings from the life of the seer after her husband and children are inoculated from the envy of men and their hatred by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-قراءة-القرآن-الكريم-في-المنام?page=1387" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-قراءة-القرآن-في-المنام?page=981" > reading the Holy Quran </a> </a> and the legal Ruqyah, so she purifies her home free from deceit and conspiracy. </p>
<p>The vision also portends the arrival of many happy events in the near future, due to the success of her children and their acquisition of the highest academic qualifications and important positions, so that she becomes the first to be proud of them and people praise her for them. Her good morals and wonderful life, but some believe that the dream is a bad sign of her husband marrying another woman, so she should be careful, and God knows best. </p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
